  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nWhen debugging a transition problem from a fuzzed state, I found that the `teku transition` command was unable to read the pre-state because it started as a Bellatrix state (_i.e.,_ `altairForkEpoch=0` and `bellatrixForkEpoch=0`). I needed to modify some things to get it working. I would have appreciated an option for this. Thoughts?",
