    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "You can achieve this by using the `--network` option and pointing to a custom network config file (https://github.com/ConsenSys/teku/blob/eedecbfb66a397fd3dabe2b9375d9f62990af951/ethereum/spec/src/main/resources/tech/pegasys/teku/spec/config/configs/mainnet.yaml is the mainnet one - should be pretty much identical to what the spec has).\r\n\r\nYou can also override them with the `--Xnetwork-bellatrix-fork-epoch` and `--Xnetwork-altair-fork-epoch` options. Everything in `Eth2NetworkOptions` (https://github.com/ConsenSys/teku/blob/3e0a11f84dea4eb98fbf35fe1abf9d309cf30269/teku/src/main/java/tech/pegasys/teku/cli/options/Eth2NetworkOptions.java) can be used with the transition commands.\r\n\r\nDoes that cover what you need?",
